  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship Exhaust Modifier</span>.<br><br>A visual enhancement for the starship, replacing traditional exhaust jets with a plasma thruster and generating a dramatic plume of ionized matter.<br><br>Install this <span class=\"name name-technology\">technology</span> in your starship inventory to change the appearance of the engine exhaust trails.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船排气管修改器</span>。<br><br>一种飞船的视觉增强装置，用等离子推进器取代传统的排气喷射器，会产生壮丽的离子化物质尾迹。<br><br>在你的飞船库存中安装这个<span class=\"name name-technology\">技术</span>以改变驱动器排气管尾迹的外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船排氣管改造器</span>。<br><br>強化太空船的視覺效果，用電漿推進器取代傳統的噴射口，產生大量的離子物質氣流。<br><br>安裝此<span class=\"name name-technology\">科技</span>到你的太空船道具欄，改變引擎廢氣尾跡的外觀。"
  },
